  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Floor Supervisor (F&B)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Introduction:</strong></p><p>temper. is where bold flavors, craft cocktails, and a lively atmosphere meet. We’re on the lookout for a Floor Supervisor who can keep the energy buzzing, ensure flawless service, and make every guest feel like the star of the night.</p><p>If you thrive in a fast-paced, hands-on environment, love leading a tight-knit team, and enjoy delivering unforgettable dining experiences, this is your next adventure.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></p><ul><li>Together with the Management, lead the front-of-house team during service, ensuring smooth operations from guest seating to timing each course and drink perfectly</li><li>Welcome and impress guests, manage reservations, seating, and special requests with warmth and professionalism.</li><li>Maintain high service standards, guest comfort, and an upbeat restaurant vibe that keeps energy levels high.</li><li>Coordinate closely with kitchen and bar teams to ensure seamless timing of dishes, drinks, and guest requests.</li><li>Uphold hygiene, safety, and cleanliness standards, keeping the dining space inviting at all times.</li><li>Handle guest feedback with grace, turning challenges into memorable experiences.</li></ul><p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>2–3 years in a supervisory or senior server role, ideally in fine dining, high-end casual, or grill-focused restaurants.</li><li>Hands-on, confident, and able to lead the floor with energy and precision.</li><li>Pre-opening experience is a strong plus.</li><li>Passionate about creating memorable guest experiences and fostering a collaborative team environment.</li></ul><p><strong>Perks of Joining Temper:</strong></p><ul><li>Medical Benefits</li><li>Meal Allowances </li><li>Birthday Leave</li><li>Group-wide discounts</li><li>5-day work week + OT</li><li>Opportunity to grow with a dynamic, high-energy team</li></ul><p>If you’re someone who thrives on running the floor, keeping energy high, and making every guest feel special, <strong>temper.</strong> wants you to join our team.</p>",
